    "chased awkwardly. After the central trade you reach the Open Sicilian, where you have a half-open c-file and a "
    "central majority to play with. 4...Nf6 hits e4 and forces 5.Nc3 to defend it. And then the move that names the "
    "whole system: 5...a6.")
